  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/54e59c6c1083bc05a3e2d4b6c395a5e3.avif?t=1731078711\" width=600 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/b6a6e4571668611c1a4fe0eb475f28d4.poster.avif?t=1731078711\" width=626 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/b6a6e4571668611c1a4fe0eb475f28d4.webm?t=1731078711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/b6a6e4571668611c1a4fe0eb475f28d4.mp4?t=1731078711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong><u>Jump, fall, crash, REPEAT!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump from one place to the other to gather all the keys! Shoot yourself through multiple rooms trying to land on tight spots. Use physics to your advantage! Get out of the house! But be wary - this ultimate jumping exercise won’t be easy. Constant falling and crashing will push your resolve and composure to the limit. Just don’t say we didn’t warn you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/247253ae75fb1b790be99cf087e87a0f.poster.avif?t=1731078711\" width=626 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/247253ae75fb1b790be99cf087e87a0f.webm?t=1731078711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/247253ae75fb1b790be99cf087e87a0f.mp4?t=1731078711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong><u>Gather keys and unlock new levels!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get through this harcore obstacle course called “house”. Sounds easy enough - right? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every room is a totally new challenge, with unique dangers, various puzzles, and of course a path that will give you a huge beating before you beat it! Good luck!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/4ddbcaa655660a433398d8909ebb3d17.poster.avif?t=1731078711\" width=626 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/4ddbcaa655660a433398d8909ebb3d17.webm?t=1731078711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/4ddbcaa655660a433398d8909ebb3d17.mp4?t=1731078711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong><u>Avoid dangers!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While getting all the keys, jumping through levels and finding new playable objects try no to die a lot. Don’t get burned, electrocuted or simply smashed on a floor by gravity. There are plenty of ways to lose here! But also plenty of ways to win!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/08b6a1cf4abae2edebf71df80ea688e0.poster.avif?t=1731078711\" width=626 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/08b6a1cf4abae2edebf71df80ea688e0.webm?t=1731078711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/08b6a1cf4abae2edebf71df80ea688e0.mp4?t=1731078711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong><u>Unlock MORE players!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go through the house and unlock all the playable pawns by interacting with (not so) random objects! Every pawn has unique physical properties and ways to use them. Figure them out and find new ways to beat your high scores!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/6160b28c2839fb3deea4b3c934c73981.poster.avif?t=1731078711\" width=626 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/6160b28c2839fb3deea4b3c934c73981.webm?t=1731078711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/6160b28c2839fb3deea4b3c934c73981.mp4?t=1731078711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Speaking of Highscores!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find new shortcuts, use new playable objects, learn precision. Beat your own highscores and check your progress on a scoreboard! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Play now!</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump through challenging levels</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather keys and unlock all the rooms in the house</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find all playable pawns</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beat your high scores</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve some puzzles</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fall</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fall even more</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crash, smash, burn</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>REPEAT</u></p></li></ul>",
